text: Nafría de Ucero is a municipality found in the province of Soria in the autonomous community of Castile and León in Spain. Part of the town is inside the Cañón del Río Lobos Natural Park. It includes the small villages of Rejas de Ucero and Valdealbín. Category:Municipalities in Castile and León Category:Settlements in Soria
title: Nafría de Ucero
